Steps:

1-	Search for tutorials to install CMAKE
2-	Search for tutorials to install GLFW

9-	Go Where the OpenGLMeshLoader repo folder u cloned is
10-	You will find a file named 'Makefile' .. open it with any text editor
11-	replace the path of ur cloned repo directory in 'CURDIR' ie: CURDIR='somewhere/OpenGLMeshLoader--master'
12-	Open terminal and cd to OpenGLMeshLoader folder
13-	type make
14-	type ./program
